BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 648.00 Td (In 5-fold cross validation:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 620.00 Td (Dataset is split into 5 parts.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 608.50 Td (Round 1: fold 1 is validation, folds 2-5 are training.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 597.00 Td (Round 2: fold 2 is validation, folds 1,3,4,5 are training.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 585.50 Td (This repeats until every fold has been validation once.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 574.00 Td (Final score = average of all validation scores.) Tj ET
