BT /F2 14 Tf 48.00 774.00 Td (Important rule) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 742.00 Td (Use training data for tuning. Use test data only once at the end for final evaluation.) Tj ET
BT /F2 18 Tf 48.00 687.00 Td (5. SVM) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 48.00 637.00 Td (Theory) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 605.00 Td (SVM means Support Vector Machine. It is commonly used for classification.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 578.00 Td (SVM finds the best boundary between classes. The best boundary is the one with the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 563.00 Td (largest margin from the closest points of each class.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 535.00 Td (Class A         margin      boundary      margin         Class B) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 523.50 Td (A A A                         |) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 512.00 Td (A A                           |) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 500.50 Td (A                             |                         B B B) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 480.00 Td (The closest points to the boundary are called support vectors.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 48.00 443.00 Td (Kernel trick) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 411.00 Td (If a straight line cannot separate classes, SVM can use a kernel to make a nonlinear) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 396.00 Td (boundary.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 369.00 Td (Common kernels:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 341.00 Td (linear    Straight boundary) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 329.50 Td (rbf       Curved boundary, most common) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 318.00 Td (poly      Polynomial boundary) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 306.50 Td (sigmoid   Neural-network-like boundary) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 48.00 276.00 Td (Important SVM hyperparameters) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 243.00 Td (C       Controls how strict the model is about mistakes.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 231.50 Td (gamma   Controls influence distance for rbf/poly/sigmoid kernels.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.4 Tf 48.00 220.00 Td (kernel  Controls boundary shape.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 199.50 Td (Small C allows more mistakes and creates a smoother boundary. Large C tries to avoid) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 184.50 Td (mistakes but can overfit.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 157.50 Td (Small gamma creates smoother boundaries. Large gamma creates complex boundaries and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 48.00 142.50 Td (can overfit.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 48.00 105.50 Td (Important: scale features) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 277.50 28.00 Td (Page 10) Tj ET
